        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001097_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001097.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" resp=\"#AL\">\n                \u003Cdiv type=\"textpart\" subtype=\"section\" n=\"A\" xml:lang=\"grc\">\n                    \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>οἱ \u003CroleName type=\"civic\" subtype=\"decurio\">δεκορίωνες\u003C/roleName>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"praenomen\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Μ\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>άρκον\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/name> \u003Cname type=\"nomen\">Οὐαλέριον\u003C/name> \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname type=\"patronymic\">Διογνήτου\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cname type=\"patronymic\">Μῆγα\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cw>υἱὸν\u003C/w> \u003Cname type=\"cognomen\">Χόρτωνα\u003C/name>\u003C/persName>                    \n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>\u003CroleName type=\"paracivic\" subtype=\"euergetes\">εὐεργέταν\u003C/roleName>\n                \u003C/ab>\n                \u003C/div>\n                \u003Cdiv type=\"textpart\" subtype=\"section\" n=\"B\" xml:lang=\"la\">\n                    \u003Cab>\n                        \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>ordo et populus \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>civit\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>atis\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Lilybit\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>anorum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \n                        \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CroleName type=\"paracivic\" subtype=\"patron\">patrono\u003C/roleName> perpetuo\n                    \u003C/ab>\n                \u003C/div>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>text according to IG\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--to Marcus Valerius Chorton (son of Diognetos Megas), for his euergetism, by the Lilybaetanians, i.e. 'hoi Dekoriones M. Oualerion Diognetou Mega huion Chortana euergetan'; CIL 10.7240 is on the reverse of the stone - not a direct transl., but much the same thing viz. 'ordo et populus civit. Lilybit patrono perpetuo'. ordo et populus is transl. of boule kai demos; cf. IG 14.273 (also IG 14.575, from Centuripe). SEG 34.951 is another inscription containing the father of this man, which implies that this is not later than Augustan, since that is, so M-P, poss. C2 BC. SEG 37 is an observation simply that Megas is a name, not a tribal. Robert and Mason note that this inscription currently seems to be the unique example of the Greek transcr. of decurio in the sense of 'bouleutes'. cf. SEG.37.1814 andBE 1961.119-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Kaibel\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1890\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\">277 \u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/Q2SBPG9F\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7240\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>34.0951\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIG\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Franz\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1853\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>5495\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/TQMVHEVL\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\">https://b